task.summary: Fixed problem with routing Renamed table cell interface to cinterface to avoid conflicts.
Changed the isAndroid check to not rely on the database setting for the user, but on the GET variable the app is passing along Fixed inital display of settings of notifications
Commit of latest prod version, supporting push for ios
Added payload callback support for iOS Fixed some styling issues
Added externalPush for Android Added externalPull for iOS Added authorization steps for using native sensors ( Google Fit/ Apple Health Kit )
Implemented new menu template Reactivated rightside drawer Fixed issues with swiping left and right
